{
  "stem": "11797.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when I was-- and I only weighed maybe 70-some pounds.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I weighed maybe close to 80 pounds, I weighed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was so skinny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father and my brother, we were-- my-- my brother helped us quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I want to mention that too, now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was became a [? yarner. ?] He fixed the Germans', the SS, their socks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He knows how to fix socks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That the hole in the heel, or something else, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave him some yarn and a big needle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he did that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He learned how to-- you know-- and they used to give him bread, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he used to-- he used to help.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I want to stress that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because without his helping, we probably would have been dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and then he also used to catch rats, my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to call him the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- And what did he do with them?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Catch-- you know, the rats, there, you know, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a lot of rats you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He used to always, now, take a-- a whip and have to catch-- catch the rats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- but the most important thing that he was-- was he was-- what do you call it-- the yarn make-- that he fixed-- and that he was darning the socks now.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was a very big help for us now.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they used-- they used to give him bread, now, the SS, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they gave him shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not shoes, no, coffee or soup, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was able to give it to us now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because they shared together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he was like a savior to us, the younger brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
